text: Andrei Bogdanov (born 7 October 1992) is a Russian luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Russia Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
